Package com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message.resthttp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeleteMessage
    Represents an OutMessage with the method type as DELETE that will be sent to the server.
    GetMessage
    Represents an OutMessage with the method type as GET that will be sent to the server.
    Header
    Represents a http header that may be sent in the request or received back in the response.
    HeadMessage
    Represents a HEAD http call that can be made to the server.
    MultiPartGetMessage
    Represents an OutMessage with the method type as GET and that will be sent to the server to download a file from it.
    PayLoadMessage
    An abstract representation of the OutMessage that will be sent to the server with payload data in the request.
    PostMessage
    Represents an OutMessage with the method type as POST that will be sent to the server.
    PutMessage
    Represents an OutMessage with the method type as PUT that will be sent to the server.
    QueryParams
    Represents list of query parameters that can be sent in a request to the server.
    Resource
    A class that represents the resource section in a REST URL
